properties.text:
[color=#ffff00]Objective:[/color]
Each player should drop their cage in order to capture as many rats as they can. A round has 60s and players have only one chance to drop their cage.

[color=#ffff00]Controls:[/color]
[color=#ff5555]Player 1:[/color] [color=#ffff00]\[Z][/color] to move the cage and [color=#ffff00]\[X][/color] to drop it.
[color=#55ffff]Player 2:[/color]  [color=#ffff00]\[O][/color] to move the cage and [color=#ffff00]\[P][/color] to drop it.

Press [color=#ffff00]\[Space][/color] to drop the cheese...
